I created a TCP server that is based on the Java Tutorial KnockKnock server.  
When I started the JMeter TCP sampler the connection was established, however 
the input line became null in the following code of the server:

  while ((inputLine = in.readLine()) != null) {
             outputLine = kkp.processInput(inputLine);
             System.out.println("2 Input line=" + inputLine + " Output Line=" 
+ outputLine);
             if (outputLine.equals("Bye."))
                break;
        }

Therefore the endless loop was broken and no testing was performed.
